WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.399 --> 00:00:03.470
Hey, good morning family, how are y'all doing today?

00:00:03.945 --> 00:00:06.319
Praise the Lord, it's me.

00:00:06.554 --> 00:00:12.493
I don't have my dynamic duo today; she's busy, but I'm going to go ahead and do this video with y'all because I'm running late.

00:00:12.955 --> 00:00:17.520
I hope I get this posted today, but if I don't, I'm sorry about that.

00:00:17.800 --> 00:00:24.176
I had family come in from out of town and they wanted to visit, so we visited with them.

00:00:24.992 --> 00:01:09.000
But I've got to get these videos out because the Lord has really put it on my heart to lead you all in prayer for what's coming.

00:01:21.892 --> 00:01:49.851
We see another ministry with another scandal; it's very sad the way it's going, and it grieved me a lot over the last day or two.

00:01:49.851 --> 00:02:22.460
My wife has been reading about it and telling me about it, and I warned you this was coming.

00:02:22.460 --> 00:03:31.425
I told you back in November of last year that the Lord told me there would be great ministries that would have things uncovered, scandals that would be uncovered, and that He would raise up new faces, new generals in the army.

00:03:31.425 --> 00:04:05.480
There would be a cleaning of the house, as judgment begins in the house of the Lord first.

00:04:05.480 --> 00:04:18.060
We see that happening a lot this year.

00:04:18.060 --> 00:05:24.207
This year has been exactly what He said it would be, and I believe we're going to see more to come: major churches and major ministries that have tried to hide things they didn't want anyone knowing about.

00:05:24.207 --> 00:05:40.149
They tried to sweep it underneath the rug.

00:05:40.149 --> 00:05:54.800
Sadly, we're all human and we all mess up.

00:05:54.800 --> 00:06:41.400
When our lives are on display, it's easier for others to judge and point fingers because these leaders have such a platform and influence in the world.

00:06:41.400 --> 00:06:54.320
So we just show grace; that's what we do.

00:06:54.320 --> 00:07:13.503
Yeah, it hurts the body of Christ, but we just keep standing.

00:07:13.503 --> 00:08:06.020
No matter who we see fall around us, no matter how shocked we are, it's going to happen more and more because the body of Christ went to a seeker-friendly message, not a holiness and fire message.

00:08:06.020 --> 00:08:36.565
Walking with the fire and the glory is what changes you; we go from glory to glory to glory.

00:08:36.565 --> 00:09:36.794
But when we put up a hand to the Holy Spirit and don't allow Him to change us because of pride, money, or influence from social media awards, we get a big head in ministry.

00:09:36.794 --> 00:09:50.748
A lot of times it's like what the Lord spoke to Diana when He said, 'You were so used to coming to Me for a word every day, and then all of a sudden you automatically assume what I'm going to say.

00:09:50.748 --> 00:10:25.625
' I paraphrase, but you see a lot of ministries that no longer feel they have to have that fresh fire every day because they're running on fumes.

00:10:25.625 --> 00:10:44.868
It allows the enemy to find an inroad to distract and destroy you.

00:10:44.868 --> 00:11:17.369
So first and foremost, you always have to have your guard up with the blood, communion, and seeking Him.

00:11:17.369 --> 00:11:46.491
I don't know these people personally, but the Lord said to me, 'Don't go on certain platforms.

00:11:50.445 --> 00:12:12.519
I want you to be separate unto Me for a season because I'm cleaning house for your ministry.

00:12:12.519 --> 00:12:36.570
' So I've just stayed to myself and I will continue to do so until the Lord releases me.

00:12:47.613 --> 00:12:58.102
He said, 'I want you right now to keep planting your roots and go deeper with Me.

00:12:58.102 --> 00:13:36.339
Enjoy life and find that place of happiness in everything you do—with your kids, your wife, your flowers, or your dog.

00:13:36.339 --> 00:14:00.835
' God is in everything and He made all things richly for you to enjoy.

00:14:00.835 --> 00:14:23.610
Ladies and gentlemen, I want you today to enjoy life and the Thanksgiving that's coming up in America.

00:14:23.610 --> 00:15:11.120
We get so distracted by the pressure of performance and trying to succeed, but whenever the rubber meets the road and you are standing before the Father, there will be nothing there other than you and Him.

00:15:11.120 --> 00:16:08.200
If you spend your whole life trying to build your kingdom and not His, what matters most when you take your last breath is your relationship with Jesus Christ—not how much money, cars, or jewelry you have.

00:16:08.200 --> 00:16:56.040
It's the relationship you had with Him from Monday through Sunday in the mundane when nobody else is looking—not behind a camera, not on Instagram or Facebook.

00:16:56.040 --> 00:17:01.779
That's all fake anyway.

00:17:01.779 --> 00:17:16.260
Most people are just posting a story, but their lives are falling apart.

00:17:20.728 --> 00:18:06.360
They put on a facade that everything's beautiful: 'Hashtag, I've got my piña colada in my hand and I'm resting on the beach,' but the life is falling apart without the selfie.

00:18:22.520 --> 00:18:23.919
It's so self-absorbed.

00:18:23.919 --> 00:19:02.679
That's why I hate social media because it's so fake.

00:19:08.480 --> 00:19:47.861
You get a call from someone weeping who is ready to do themselves in, yet you just saw a hashtag saying everything was great.

00:19:47.861 --> 00:20:24.040
People just need to be real because they're hurting inside, and only the Lord Jesus Christ can fix that.

00:20:24.040 --> 00:21:34.889
No matter how much money or success you find, or even a good-looking spouse—she's a 10 out of 10 but she has issues, or he's a 10 out of 10 but he's abusive—people are still looking for that perfect 10.

00:21:34.889 --> 00:21:44.344
Where is your heart with the Father?

00:21:44.344 --> 00:22:17.984
When it all comes to the end, you're going to stand before Him butt-naked, basically—stripped of pride and ego.

00:22:17.984 --> 00:22:49.880
Will your works stand in the refiner's fire as pure gold, or will they burn up like stubble?

00:22:49.880 --> 00:22:54.525
Did you do things for attention, like hashtagging a five-dollar gift, or did you do it because Jesus told you to?

00:22:54.525 --> 00:23:03.347
You'll know their fruit by the tasting.

00:23:10.093 --> 00:23:12.586
You can see the fruit on the tree.

00:23:12.586 --> 00:23:48.279
As Joyce Meyer said, an apple tree doesn't have to scream that it's an apple tree; it just is what it is.

00:23:48.279 --> 00:24:09.520
I don't have to try to fake the Holy Ghost.

00:24:18.880 --> 00:24:44.564
You can't live off of yesterday's revelation or anointing; you have to have a fresh touch every day.

00:24:44.564 --> 00:25:01.670
If you try to live off an old revelation, that water becomes stagnant.

00:25:02.115 --> 00:25:19.159
I want authentic with the Holy Spirit on a day-to-day basis.

00:25:30.484 --> 00:25:57.300
We try to bring what we have at home to you, but it's different through the camera when people judge you and don't know the Holy Spirit.

00:25:57.300 --> 00:26:21.526
You might have head knowledge from a sermon five years ago, but you don't know Him at all.

00:26:28.799 --> 00:26:36.420
I'm trying to help you fall in love with Him today.

00:26:48.298 --> 00:27:12.274
Do not put your relationship in somebody on TV or YouTube, because we're all human and we all have issues.

00:27:18.288 --> 00:27:18.456
I'm a work in progress.

00:27:18.456 --> 00:27:33.893
My wife tells me all the time, 'We're a work in progress, Brandon.

00:27:33.893 --> 00:28:18.620
' We may fall or stub our knee, but we pick ourselves back up like a beanbag clown that's standing on the inside.

00:28:18.620 --> 00:28:29.264
Are you standing on the inside?

00:28:29.264 --> 00:28:44.112
That's all that matters—not what your pastor or outside family says.

00:28:44.112 --> 00:29:25.080
Sometimes you have to cut yourself off from those who have a strong influence but try to lead you in another direction.

00:29:41.895 --> 00:29:55.044
It's time to shake off those beggar clothes like blind Bartimaeus on the side of the road.

00:29:55.044 --> 00:30:30.600
When he took off that cloak and gave everything to Jesus, he stood up and received his sight.

00:30:30.600 --> 00:30:39.208
Are you spiritually blind, Bartimaeus?

00:30:39.208 --> 00:31:09.584
Is it time for you to receive your sight and have the eyes of your understanding enlightened?

00:31:09.584 --> 00:31:31.666
Take off that cloak and say, 'Jesus, I need you today.

00:31:31.666 --> 00:31:48.409
' Don't be moved by everything on social media.

00:31:48.829 --> 00:32:31.340
The Lord told me He's cleaning house and it's going to get painful because some of your idols will let you down.

00:32:31.340 --> 00:32:48.143
You've got to have Jesus on that pedestal.

00:32:53.467 --> 00:33:34.039
I learned a long time ago working for big ministers that I saw them have the biggest flesh farts you've ever seen.

00:33:34.039 --> 00:34:01.226
It can crush you, but if you have a relationship with Him, it's beautiful.

00:34:01.226 --> 00:34:15.648
He is beautiful beyond description, too marvelous for words.

00:34:19.742 --> 00:34:20.520
I stand in awe of You.

00:34:20.520 --> 00:34:49.205
Regarding investments, I told you what Kim said about the X and the P.

00:34:49.205 --> 00:35:26.373
If you are a student of investments, it's pretty obvious what I believe he was talking about.

00:35:26.373 --> 00:36:00.696
I miss the timing sometimes because I assume how quickly He is saying it.

00:36:01.274 --> 00:36:46.220
I saw an X and a P in a dream, and that is going to be a very profound investment.

00:36:46.220 --> 00:37:10.525
Abraham waited twenty years for his promise, so don't get weary in well-doing.

00:37:10.525 --> 00:37:29.480
When the full manifestation comes with $10,000 per XRP, you'll see.

00:37:29.480 --> 00:38:08.240
He spoke to me about the Dinar and the angel with sapphire blue eyes who told me, 'Shh, they can't hear what you're saying.

00:38:08.240 --> 00:38:54.207
' No matter how much I yelled in the visitation, friends and family couldn't see me because they didn't get the word for themselves.

00:38:54.207 --> 00:39:19.607
They're looking like a cow at a new gate, chewing its cud.

00:39:20.760 --> 00:40:08.640
I saw everyone who invested in a certain thing, which was the Iraqi Dinar, standing on a Persian rug when it was pulled out from under them and they lost everything.

00:40:08.640 --> 00:40:48.547
There was a 1929-style financial crash, but those who put their money in the copper pot—the one with writing about the new change—were okay.

00:40:48.547 --> 00:41:03.900
Everything you know can change in a 24-hour period.

00:41:13.187 --> 00:41:49.733
I believe a crash is coming, but there's a season of grace after the election for a great acceleration before the house of cards falls due to credit card and housing debt.

00:41:50.160 --> 00:41:59.920
I saw the interest rates freeze bank accounts.

00:41:59.920 --> 00:42:13.431
I've asked the Lord to give us more time.

00:42:13.431 --> 00:42:31.229
Then Putin used those extra-strength rockets that shook the world.

00:42:31.229 --> 00:42:48.400
I saw a massive radius by Warsaw in Poland.

00:43:05.060 --> 00:43:14.485
They used a weapon no man has ever seen that vaporized people without wiping out buildings.

00:43:14.485 --> 00:43:31.580
It's not nuclear, but it will shake nations with fear.

00:43:31.580 --> 00:43:55.200
Then I saw a major draft coming in the United States because of an attack.

00:43:58.310 --> 00:44:37.359
I saw the old Cuban Missile Crisis alliances trying to bring forth a third world war with conventional weapons more powerful than those in World War II.

00:44:41.599 --> 00:45:33.571
I saw Israel striking Iran's oil refineries, causing oil to go above $200 a barrel and gas to hit $8 or $9 a gallon with lines like the 1970s.

00:45:33.571 --> 00:45:47.720
This was used to push a green agenda.

00:45:47.720 --> 00:45:57.090
Can we change this as watchmen?

00:46:08.795 --> 00:46:26.786
We see Netanyahu talking on the news about striking refineries if they come after us again.

00:46:28.090 --> 00:46:41.205
I saw oil reserves in the Mediterranean that are ginormous.

00:46:52.420 --> 00:47:00.704
We see Trump's company wanting to buy a crypto exchange called BB something.

00:47:00.704 --> 00:47:17.600
We're going to be the most pro-crypto country with Elon Musk.

00:47:17.600 --> 00:47:40.014
They have a plan to eliminate the national debt, perhaps with gold or Bitcoin.

00:47:40.619 --> 00:48:03.105
The angel told me, 'They're not dead, they don't see it.

00:48:03.105 --> 00:48:11.739
' We're going to pray.

00:48:17.650 --> 00:48:31.920
I don't try to prepare anything; this is just overflow.

00:48:36.419 --> 00:48:57.275
Father, we thank You for Your hand on this YouTube channel and every person represented here.

00:49:13.260 --> 00:49:13.520
We believe they receive Your divine protection and healing.

00:49:15.499 --> 00:49:43.488
We pray Elon Musk has a radical conversion like the next Billy Graham and helps bring forth the end-time harvest money.

00:49:43.488 --> 00:50:14.549
We thank You for a supernatural debt cancellation seed for America through Elon or President Trump.

00:50:14.549 --> 00:50:49.778
I pray for supernatural protection over President Trump and his cabinet, that he would put people of integrity around him.

00:50:49.778 --> 00:51:14.780
May we be a nation that says 'In God We Trust' with all our hearts.

00:51:14.780 --> 00:51:30.410
Father, judgment begins in the house of the Lord first.

00:51:43.571 --> 00:51:52.987
We bring in the new Davids with the brand new anointing.

00:51:52.987 --> 00:52:02.439
Stir up the flames within us.

00:52:02.439 --> 00:52:39.686
We're not lazy, looking for someone else to feed us like an infant; we get out and go be scavengers of the Word.

00:52:39.686 --> 00:53:00.032
If it doesn't witness with you, then click off.

00:53:00.032 --> 00:53:23.920
But we thank You for the Holy Spirit flowing like a mighty rushing river.

00:53:23.920 --> 00:53:45.891
Just as Andrew Wommack says, stop chasing your tail; you've already got it.

00:53:49.119 --> 00:54:07.700
We call peace over this war and ask for an extended time of grace.

00:54:07.700 --> 00:54:25.119
We ask for a supernatural move of the Holy Spirit in these last days.

00:54:25.119 --> 00:54:43.826
We pray Joe Biden does not cause any escalation in this war.

00:54:43.826 --> 00:54:53.674
We call confusion in the enemy's camp.

00:54:53.674 --> 00:55:15.144
What will you do with these four years until the next Shemitah cycle?

00:55:25.729 --> 00:55:32.250
We give You all the glory, honor, and praise.

00:55:32.250 --> 00:55:34.100
Amen.

00:55:34.100 --> 00:55:59.360
Subscribe if you haven't and click the notification bell and like button for the algorithm.

00:56:03.503 --> 00:56:17.960
We believe Jesus Christ is a healer and the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:56:17.960 --> 00:56:34.741
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:56:34.741 --> 00:56:39.716
We will see you tomorrow.

00:56:39.716 --> 00:56:40.931
Bye-bye.
